what it is; bullet, homing laser, satellite laser cannon-- same color = invincibility.  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Opposite colors however, kill in one hit.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Trick is... well... you can see for yourself how this becomes INSANELY difficult with this Java applet demo:<br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> NOTE</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->: the applet takes roughly <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 5 minutes</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> on a 56.6k modem to load, but once it's up, you can select any one of the 10 play scenarios immediately.  You don't shoot, but the mouse moves the cursor, left mouse button switches modes &amp; same rules apply<br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> dark=dark, light=light, dark kills light, light kills dark.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Good luck.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> unofficial Ikaruga Gameplay Test (japanese only)</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~cs8k-cyu/bulletml/narihira/narihira_applet.html">www.asahi-net.or.jp/~cs8k...pplet.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Here's something to savor even more!  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> The first stage theme on mp3!</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://perso.wanadoo.fr/didier.delbrayelle/kevin/ikaruga.html">perso.wanadoo.fr/didier.d...aruga.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>And that's that.  Goodnight, Seattle.<br>-TBW<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showNextMessage?topicID=146.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=146.topic><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br>